91 (C) Reinstatement of full fringe benefits and seniority rights;
92 (D) Compensation for lost wages, benefits, and other remuneration; and
93 (E) Any other compensatory damages allowable at law.
94 (f) A court may award reasonable attorney's fees, court costs, and expenses to a prevailing
95 person, including, but not limited to, an independent contractor or public employee.
